00:15:01.030 --> 00:15:05.910
So it's every child -- many people have more
than one kid there -- every child, every instance,

00:15:05.910 --> 00:15:08.810
you're paying a fine.
This fine will be calculated monthly.

00:15:08.810 --> 00:15:11.070
It is to be paid together with the regular
monthly payment.

00:15:11.070 --> 00:15:18.340
Sincerely, the manager of the day-care center."
So of course, tell me your first name. Patsy?

