00:16:08.490 --> 00:16:11.840
happened?
The incident -- no! -- it didn't go down!

00:16:11.840 --> 00:16:15.290
The incidents of lateness stayed up.
You did permanent damage.

00:16:15.290 --> 00:16:18.780
Now, this is -- seems on the surface as we
think about things.

00:16:18.780 --> 00:16:24.010
