Let's talk about this company, yes.

00:25:05.570 --> 00:25:10.299
This company -- Atlassian. Atlassian -- Australian
company.

00:25:10.299 --> 00:25:13.279
Software company. Obviously much smaller than
Google.

00:25:13.279 --> 00:25:16.169
Atlassian. Has some offices in San Francisco
